name: Mercurial #1: Mercurial Serpent
description:
The Mercurial series is a set of works inspired by the Mercury/Hermes archetype, symbologies and the alchemy relate, inspirated in medieval pictures of the C. G. Jung book "Psycologie et Alchimie'

The snake in alchemy is the “mercurial serpent”, the old Gnostic image for the Nous, the mind, where the spirit was represented as a serpent, as the Agathodaemon (the good daemon), or directly called the serpent of the Nous. ~Carl Jung, ETH, Alchemy,
